    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "text": "Explore the lineup and reserve yours today.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "36px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Available for a limited time when you get an approved financing offer for 60 months by March 31.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "500",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "20px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Available when you lease a new2026 R1 Dual with Max battery and Performance Upgrade for 24 or 36 months.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "500",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "20px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "All-electric, 7-seat SUV built for making memories.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(21, 21, 21)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "From $76,990 \u00b7 Est. $899/mo\u00b3 | EPA est. range 410 mi\u2074",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Everything you need to get out there and say yes to new things.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(21, 21, 21)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Available spring 2026",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "All-electric truck built for whatever you call a road.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(21, 21, 21)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "From $72,990 \u00b7 Est. $899/mo\u00b3 | EPA est. range 420 mi\u2074",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "From intuitive software to smart headlights to mobile app, Rivians are equipped with technology that helps make driving safer, easier and more fun.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Powerful, efficient, truly a joy to drive. Built to go anywhere, on-road and off \u2014  with up to 9 drive modes that optimize for the terrain at the touch of a button.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "From innovative storage (yes, there\u2019s a tunnel for gear in the truck) to elevated interiors inspired by nature, every detail is dialed in.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "The R1S continues to earn awards for safety \u2014\u00a0most recently, a 2026 TOP SAFETY PICK+ from the IIHS for the 2026 R1S.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "20px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "2617 NE 46th StreetSeattle, WA 98105",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "20px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Mon\u2013Sat: 10:00am\u20138:00pmSun: 11:00am\u20136:00pm",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(0, 0, 0)",
          "lineHeight": "20px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Get behind",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "56px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "60px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "the wheel",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "56px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "60px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "56px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "60px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "With up to 420 miles of range and a NACS charge port so you can charge in more places, Rivian makes it easy to get out and explore.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "20px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Access to over 50,000 chargers \u2014\u00a0including Tesla Superchargers.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Built-in technology takes the guesswork out of trip planning.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "With a Wall Charger at home, you\u2019ll always wake up ready to go.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "24px",
          "fontWeight": "600",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "As software-defined vehicles, Rivians are designed to evolve. We can add new features with software updates  (just like a phone) so your vehicle actually improves over time.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "More fully electric adventure is  on the way. Sign up to follow along.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "32px",
          "fontWeight": "500",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "36px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Subscribe",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "500",
          "color": "rgb(99, 99, 99)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "1 / 1",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "16px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(21, 21, 21)",
          "lineHeight": "24px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "By submitting, I agree to receive future communications from Rivian and I have read and agree to Rivian's Terms and acknowledge the Data Privacy Notice.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "11px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "17px"
        }
      },
      {
        "text": "Everything we do is in service of building the future that our kids\u2019 kids' kids deserve and preserving the natural world for generations to come.",
        "styles": {
          "fontSize": "20px",
          "fontWeight": "400",
          "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
          "lineHeight": "28px"
        }
      },
